div class=\"list-banner clear\">\n            <div class=\"img\"></div>\n            <div class=\"pic\">    <img src=\"../../images/list-banner.png\">\n</div>\n        </div>\n        <!-- list-banner end -->\n        <div class=\"list wrap clear\">\n            <div class=\"list-l fl\">\n                <div class=\"position\">\n                    <p>    <a href=\"../../index.htm\">首页</a>\n    &gt;\n    <a href=\"../../szzk/jzgml.htm\">师资状况</a>\n    &gt;\n    <a href=\"../../szzk/jzgml.htm\">教职工名录</a>\n    &gt;\n    <a href=\"../../szzk/jzgml/jsjwlyjs.htm\">计算机网络研究所</a>\n    &gt;\n    <a href=\"../../szzk/jzgml/jsjwlyjs/zg.htm\">正高</a>\n    &gt;\n    正文\n</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"show\">\n\n\n\n\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/interface/NewsvoteDWR.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/engine.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/newscontent.js\"></script><link href=\"/system/resource/js/photoswipe/3.0.5.1/photoswipe.css\" type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/photoswipe/3.0.5.1/klass.min.js\"></script><link rel=\"stylesheet\" content-type=\"text/css\" href=\"/system/resource/style/component/news/content/format2.css\"><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/ajax.js\"></script><form name=\"_newscontent_fromname\"><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/jquery/jquery-latest.min.js\"></script>\n<div>\n    <div class=\"show01\">\n    <h5>李丹</h5>\n   \n    </div>\n    <table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" border=\"0\" align=\"center\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse;display:none;\">\n            <tbody><tr>\n                <td width=\"20%\" style=\"border:1px solid gray\">职称</td>\n                <td width=\"30%\" style=\"border:1px solid gray\">教授</td>\n            \n            \n                <td width=\"20%\" style=\"border:1px solid gray\">电话</td>\n                <td width=\"30%\" style=\"border:1px solid gray\"></td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td width=\"20%\" style=\"border:1px solid gray\">邮箱</td>\n                <td width=\"30%\" style=\"border:1px solid gray\">tolidan@tsinghua.edu.cn</td>\n            </tr>\n    </tbody></table>\n    <div id=\"vsb_content_2\" class=\"show02\"><div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_img\"><img src=\"/__local/3/7D/1F/13217AB86A48AF5F2638B8308B5_8818C00E_15A82.jpg\" width=\"302\" vsbhref=\"vurl\" vurl=\"/_vsl/37D1F13217AB86A48AF5F2638B8308B5/8818C00E/15A82\" vheight=\"\" vwidth=\"302\" orisrc=\"/__local/3/7D/1F/13217AB86A48AF5F2638B8308B5_8818C00E_15A82.jpg\" class=\"img_vsb_content\"></p>\n<p>姓名：李丹</p>\n<p>职称：教授</p>\n<p>邮箱：tolidan@tsinghua.edu.cn</p>\n<p>主页：<a href=\"http://nasp.cs.tsinghua.edu.cn/lidan.html\">http://nasp.cs.tsinghua.edu.cn/lidan.html</a></p>\n<p><strong>教育背景</strong></p>\n<p>本科 (计算机科学与技术), 北京师范大学, 中国, 2003</p>\n<p>博士 (计算机科学与技术), 清华大学, 中国, 2008</p>\n<p><strong>研究领域</strong></p>\n<p>数据中心网络，网络智能，可信任互联网</p>\n<p><strong>学术兼职</strong></p>\n<p>期刊编委：IEEE Transactions on Computers，IEEE Transactions on Wireless Communications，IEEE Transactions on Cloud Computing</p>\n<p>指导委员会：APNet</p>\n<p>程序委员会主席：APNet 2025，IEEE LANMAN 2014</p>\n<p>大会主席：APNet 2018，IEEE LANMAN 2015</p>\n<p>程序委员会委员：ACM SIGCOMM, USENIX NSDI，IEEE ICNP</p>\n<p><strong>奖励荣誉</strong></p>\n<p>IEEE Fellow，2025</p>\n<p>国家科技进步一等奖，“下一代互联网源地址验证体系结构SAVA关键技术与规模化应用”，2024</p>\n<p>中国电子学会技术发明一等奖，“基于多维感知的大规模数据中心网络路由控制技术”，2024</p>\n<p>教育部青年科学奖，2019</p>\n<p>中国通信学会技术发明一等奖，“性能可预期的大规模数据中心网络关键技术与应用”，2019</p>\n<p><strong>研究概况</strong></p>\n<p>在数据中心网络方向，主要研究数据中心网络体系结构、路由传输协议、可编程网络。以项目负责人承担国家973项目“软件定义的云数据中心网络基础理论与关键技术”。</p>\n<p>在网络智能方向，主要研究Network for AI和AI for Network，包括优化AI训练的互联拓扑、网络协议、集合通信、并行策略，以及基于AI的网络运维和网络优化方法。以项目负责人承担国家重点研发计划项目“网络资源感知的智能路由控制技术”。</p>\n<p>在可信任互联网方向，主要研究互联网源地址验证和路由安全。在IETF牵头发起成立SAVNET工作组。</p>\n<p><strong>代表性论文</strong></p>\n<p><strong>会议论文</strong></p>\n<p>[1] Fei Gui, Songtao Wang, Dan Li, Li Chen, Kaihui Gao, Congcong Min and Yi Wang, \"RedTE: Mitigating Subsecond Traffic Bursts with Real-time and Distributed Traffic Engineering\", ACM SIGCOMM 2024, Sydney, Australia.</p>\n<p>[2] Kaihui Gao, Li Chen, Dan Li, Vincent Liu, Xizheng Wang, Ran Zhang and Lu Lu, \"DONS: Fast and Affordable Discrete Event Network Simulation with Automatic Parallelization\", ACM SIGCOMM 2023, New York, USA.</p>\n<p>[3] Shuai Wang, Kaihui Gao, Kun Qian, Dan Li, Rui Miao, Bo Li, Yu Zhou, Ennan Zhai, Chen Sun, Jiaqi Gao, Dai Zhang, Binzhang Fu, Frank Kelly, Dennis Cai, Hongqiang Harry Liu and Ming Zhang, \"Predictable vFabric on Informative Data Plane\", ACM SIGCOMM 2022, Amsterdam, Netherlands.</p>\n<p>[4] Chuanxiong Guo, Guohan Lu, Dan Li, HaitaoWu, Xuan Zhang, Yunfeng Shi, Chen Tian, Yongguang Zhang and Songwu Lu, \"BCube: A High Performance, Server-centric Network Architecture for Modular Data Centers\", ACM SIGCOMM 2009, Barcelona, Spain.</p>\n<p>[5] Fei Gui, Kaihui Gao, Li Chen, Dan Li, Vincent Liu, Ran Zhang, Hongbing Yang and Dian Xiong, \"Accelerating Design Space Exploration for LLM Training Systems with Multi-experiment Parallel Simulation\", USENIX NSDI 2025, Philadelphia, PA, USA.</p>\n<p>[6] Xizheng Wang, Li Chen, Libin Liu, Dan Li, Yukai Miao and Yu Bai, \"Resolving Packets from Counters: Enabling Multi-scale Network Traffic Super Resolution via Composable Large Traffic Model\", USENIX NSDI 2025, Philadelphia, PA, USA.</p>\n<p>[7] Jianmin Liu, Li Chen, Dan Li and Yukai Miao, \"CEGS: Configuration Example Generalizing Synthesizer\", USENIX NSDI 2025, Philadelphia, PA, USA.</p>\n<p>[8] Xizheng Wang , Qingxu Li, Yichi Xu, Gang Lu, Li Chen, Dan Li, Heyang Zhou, Linkang Zheng, Sen Zhang, Yikai Zhu, Yang Liu, Pengcheng Zhang, Kun Qian, Ennan Zhai, Dennis Cai and Binzhang Fu, \"SimAI: Unifying Architecture Design and Performance Tunning for Large-Scale Large Language Model Training with Scalability and Precision\", USENIX NSDI 2025, Philadelphia, PA, USA.</p>\n<p>[9] Tianfeng Liu, Yangrui Chen, Dan Li, Chuan Wu, Yibo Zhu, Jun He, Yanghua Peng, Hongzheng Chen, Hongzhi Chen and Chuanxiong Guo, \"BGL: GPU-Efficient GNN Training by Optimizing Graph Data I/O and Preprocessing\", USENIX NSDI 2023, Boston, MA, USA.</p>\n<p>[10] Yanshu Wang, Dan Li, Yuanwei Lu, Jianping Wu, Hua Shao and Yutian Wang, \"Elixir: A High-performance and Low-cost Approach to Managing Hardware/Software Hybrid Flow Tables Considering Flow Burstiness\", USENIX NSDI 2022, Virtual.</p>\n<p>[11] Kaihui Gao, Chen Sun, Shuai Wang, Dan Li, Yu Zhou, Hongqiang Harry Liu, Lingjun Zhu and Ming Zhang, \"Buffer-based End-to-end Request Event Monitoring in the Cloud\", USENIX NSDI 2022, Virtual.</p>\n<p>[12] Dawei Wang, Geng Zhou, Xianglong Li, Yu Bai, Li Chen, Ting Qin, Jian Sun, Dan Li, \"The Digital Cybersecurity Expert: How Far Have We Come?\", IEEE S&amp;P 2025, San Francisco, CA, USA.</p>\n<p>[13] Dawei Wang, Geng Zhou, Li Chen, Dan Li and Yukai Miao, \"ProphetFuzz: Fully Automated Prediction and Fuzzing of High-Risk Option Combinations with Only Documentation via Large Language Model\", ACM CCS 2024, Salt Lake City, UT, USA.</p>\n<p>[14] Lancheng Qin, Dan Li, Ruifeng Li and Kang Wang, \"Accelerating the Detection of Route Origin Hijacking by Distinguishing Legitimate and Illegitimate MOAS\", USENIX Security 2022, Boston, MA, USA.</p>\n<p>[15] Lancheng Qin, Li Chen, Dan Li, Honglin Ye and Yutian Wang, \"Understanding ROV Deployment in the Real World and Why MANRS Action 1 Is Not Followed\", ISOC NDSS 2024, San Diego, CA, USA.</p>\n<p><strong>期刊论文</strong></p>\n<p>[1] Jianmin Liu, Dan Li and Yongjun Xu, \"Deep Distributional Reinforcement Learning-based Adaptive Routing with Guaranteed Delay Bounds\", IEEE/ACM Transactions on Networking, 32(6):4692-4706, 2024.</p>\n<p>﻿[2] Kaihui Gao, ﻿Shuai Wang, Kun Qian, Dan Li, Rui Miao, Bo Li, Yu Zhou, Ennan Zhai, Chen Sun, Jiaqi Gao, Dai Zhang, Binzhang Fu, Frank Kelly, Dennis Cai, Hongqiang Harry Liu, Yan Li, Hongwei Yang and Tao Sun, \"Dependable Virtualized Fabric on Programmable Data Plane\", IEEE/ACM Transactions on Networking, 31(4):1748-1764, 2023.</p>\n<p>[3] ﻿Kaihui Gao, Chen Sun, Shuai Wang, Dan Li, Yu Zhou, Hongqiang Harry Liu, Lingjun Zhu, Ming Zhang, Xiang Deng, Cheng Zhou and Lu Lu, \"Buffer-based High-coverage and Low-overhead Request Event Monitoring in the Cloud\", IEEE/ACM Transactions on Networking, 31(4):1732-1747, 2023.</p>\n<p>[4] Shuai Wang, Jinkun Geng and Dan Li, \"Impact of Synchronization Topology on DML Performance: Both Logical Topology and Physical Topology\", IEEE/ACM Transactions on Networking, 30(2):572-585, 2022.</p>\n<p>[5] Songtao Wang, Dan Li, Yang Cheng, Jinkun Geng, Yanshu Wang, Shuai Wang, Shutao Xia and Jianping Wu, \"A Scalable, High-performance and Fault-tolerant Network Architecture for Distributed Machine Learning\", IEEE/ACM Transactions on Networking, 28(4):1752-1764, 2020.</p>\n<p>[6] Xuya Jia, Dan Li, Jing Zhu and Yong Jiang, \"Metro: An Efficient Traffic Fast Rerouting Scheme With Low Overhead\", IEEE/ACM Transactions on Networking, 27(5):2015-2027, 2019.</p>\n<p>[7] Guo Chen, Youjian Zhao, Hailiang Xu, Dan Pei and Dan Li, \"F2Tree: Rapid Failure Recovery for Routing in Production Data Center Networks\", IEEE/ACM Transactions on Networking, 25(4):1940-1953, 2017.</p>\n<p>[8] Ming Zhu, Dan Li, Fangxin Wang, Anke Li, K.K. Ramakrishnan, Ying Liu, Jianping Wu, Nan Zhu and Xue Liu, \"CCDN: Content-Centric Data Center Networks\", IEEE/ACM Transactions on Networking, 24(6):3537-3550, 2016.</p>\n<p>[9] Dan Li, Yirong Yu, Junxiao Shi and Beichuan Zhang, \"PALS: Saving Network Power With Low Overhead to ISPs and Applications\", IEEE/ACM Transactions on Networking, 24(5):2913–2925, 2016.</p>\n<p>[10] Dan Li, Jing Zhu, Jianping Wu, Junjie Guan and Ying Zhang, \"Guaranteeing Heterogeneous Bandwidth Demand in Multi-tenant Data Center Networks\", IEEE/ACM Transactions on Networking, 23(5):1648-1660, 2015.</p>\n<p>[11] Dan Li, Hongze Zhao, Mingwei Xu and Xiaoming Fu, \"Revisiting the Design of Mega Data Centers: Considering Heterogeneity among Containers\", IEEE/ACM Transactions on Networking, 22(5):1503-1515, 2014.</p>\n<p>[12] Dan Li, Yuanjie Li, Jianping Wu, Sen Su and Jiangwei Yu, \"ESM: Efficient and Scalable Data Center Multicast Routing\", IEEE/ACM Transactions on Networking, 20(3):944-955, 2012.</p>\n<p>[13] Dan Li, Jianping Wu, Jiangchuan Liu, Yong Cui and Ke Xu, \"Defending against Distance Cheating in Link-weighted Application Layer Multicast\", IEEE/ACM Transactions on Networking, 19(5):1448-1457, 2011.</p>\n<p>[14] Dan Li, Chuanxiong Guo, Haitao Wu, Kun Tan, Yongguang Zhang, Songwu Lu and Jianping Wu, \"Scalable and Cost-effective Interconnection of Data-center Servers using Dual Server Ports\", IEEE/ACM Transactions on Networking, 19(1):102-114, 2011.</p>\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">[15] Dan Li, Yunfei Shang and Congjie Chen, \"EXR: Greening Data Center Network with Software Defined Exclusive Routing\", IEEE Transactions on Computers, 64(9):2534-2544, 2015.</p>\n</div></div><div id=\"div_vote_id\"></div>\n        <div class=\"show03\">\n    <p>上一篇：<a href=\"3586.htm\">刘卫东</a></p>\n    <p>下一篇：<a href=\"3585.htm\">任丰原</a></p>\n     </div>\n    <p align=\"right\">【<a href=\"javascript:window.opener=null;window.open('','_self');window.close();\">关闭</a>】</p>\n</div>\n</form>\n</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"list-r fr\">\n                <div class=\"list-nav\">\n                    <h5><a>\n\n\n\n师资状况</a></h5>\n                    <p></p>\n                    <div class=\"pic\"><img src=\"../../images/list-nav04.png\"></div>\n                                        <ul>\n\t<li class=\"onn\">\n\t\t<a href=\"../../szzk/jzgml.htm\" title=\"教职工名录\">教职工名录</a>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t\t<a href=\"../../szzk/jcrc.htm\" title=\"杰出人才\">杰出人才</a>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t\t<a href=\"../../szzk/jxms.htm\" title=\"教学名师\">教学名师</a>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t\t<a href=\"../../szzk/xnjzjs.htm\" t